<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Posts on Kevin's Digital Garden</title><link>https://kediga.com/posts/</link><description>Recent content in Posts on Kevin's Digital Garden</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 19 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://kediga.com/posts/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>How to Create a Free Personal Blog Using Hugo and GitHub Pages</title><link>https://kediga.com/posts/how-to-create-a-personal-blog-using-hugo-and-github-pages/</link><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://kediga.com/posts/how-to-create-a-personal-blog-using-hugo-and-github-pages/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>I have had more spare time since I changed my job earlier this year. I have been contemplating ways to share my life and technology experiences while also enhancing my writing skills. Although Wordpress appears to be a quite popular platform for personal blogs, I&amp;rsquo;d rather not deal with ongoing expenses for servers or disruptions caused by irrelevant technical tasks like virtual machine and database configurations.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>That&amp;rsquo;s why using an open source &lt;a class="link" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Static_site_generator" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Static Site Generator&lt;/a> along with a free &lt;a class="link" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_hosting_service" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>web hosting service&lt;/a> seems like the ideal approach for me.
Here are the tools I used:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a class="link" href="https://gohugo.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>&lt;strong>Hugo&lt;/strong>&lt;/a>: An open source Static Site Generator written in Go that allows you to create fast and flexible websites such as personal blogs, company homepages, galleries and many more.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a class="link" href="https://pages.github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>&lt;strong>GitHub Pages&lt;/strong>&lt;/a>: A free web hosting service provided by GitHub that allows you to host your site directly from your GitHub repository.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>In the end, I built this site to serve as my personal blog by following the documentations of those tools. I decided to document the entire process as a future reference for myself, and for anyone else, like you, who happens to come across this post by chance.&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="installation">Installation&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>There are 3 other tools that required to be installed besides Hugo: &lt;a class="link" href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Git&lt;/a>, &lt;a class="link" href="https://go.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Go&lt;/a> and &lt;a class="link" href="https://sass-lang.com/dart-sass/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Dart Sass&lt;/a>.
I installed these tools on both my Windows 10 PC and MacBook.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="windows">Windows&lt;/h3>
&lt;h4 id="install-hugo">Install Hugo&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>I installed Chocolatey first since both Hugo and Sass can also be installed through Chocolatey easily.&lt;/p>
&lt;h5 id="install-chocolatey">Install Chocolatey&lt;/h5>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Open PowerShell as administrator and type:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-PowerShell" data-lang="PowerShell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">Get-ExecutionPolicy&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>If it returns &lt;strong>Restricted&lt;/strong>, run the following command:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-PowerShell" data-lang="PowerShell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">Set-ExecutionPolicy&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">AllSigned&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>or&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-PowerShell" data-lang="PowerShell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">Set-ExecutionPolicy&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">Bypass&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">-Scope&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">Process&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Run the following command to install Chocolatey:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-PowerShell" data-lang="PowerShell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">Set-ExecutionPolicy&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">Bypass&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">-Scope&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">Process&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">-Force&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="no">System.Net.ServicePointManager&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">SecurityProtocol&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="no">System.Net.ServicePointManager&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">SecurityProtocol&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">-bor&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">3072&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">iex &lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">((&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">New-Object&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">System&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="py">Net&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">WebClient&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">).&lt;/span>&lt;span class="py">DownloadString&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;https://community.chocolatey.org/install.ps1&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">))&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Wait for the command to complete, then confirm Chocolatey has been installed correctly:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-PowerShell" data-lang="PowerShell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">choco&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">-?&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>After installing Chocolatey, install Hugo:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-PowerShell" data-lang="PowerShell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">choco&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">install&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nb">hugo-extended&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="install-git">Install Git&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>Download the standalone installer from &lt;a class="link" href="https://git-scm.com/download/win" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>download page&lt;/a> and install it.&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="install-go">Install Go&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>Follow this &lt;a class="link" href="https://go.dev/doc/install" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>documentation&lt;/a> to download and install Go.&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="install-sass">Install Sass&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>Run following command in PowerShell:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-PowerShell" data-lang="PowerShell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">choco&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">install&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">sass&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="macos">macOS&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Install &lt;a class="link" href="https://brew.sh/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>homebrew&lt;/a> whether it is not installed yet.&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="install-hugo-1">Install Hugo&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>Open Terminal and run following command:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">brew install hugo
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="install-git-1">Install Git&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>Run following command:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">brew install git
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="install-go-1">Install Go&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>Follow this &lt;a class="link" href="https://go.dev/doc/install" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>documentation&lt;/a> to download and install Go.&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="install-sass-1">Install Sass&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>Run following command:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">brew install sass/sass/sass
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="create-a-site">Create a site&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Run following commands in PowerShell or Terminal.&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Create the directory structure in the &lt;em>mysite&lt;/em> directory:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hugo new site mysite
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Change working directory to the root of &lt;em>mysite&lt;/em>:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> mysite
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Create an empty Git repository in the working directory:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git init
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Clone the &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Stack&lt;/a> theme to the theme directory, adding it to &lt;em>mysite&lt;/em> as a Git submodule:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">git submodule add https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack/ themes/hugo-theme-stack
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Apply theme:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">echo&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;theme = &amp;#39;hugo-theme-stack&amp;#39;&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &amp;gt;&amp;gt; hugo.toml
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Now start Hugo’s development server and open the URL displayed in terminal to have a look at the site we created.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hugo server
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>Development server can be stopped by pressing &lt;strong>Ctrl&lt;/strong> + &lt;strong>C&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="add-a-post">Add a post&lt;/h2>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Add a new post to &lt;em>mysite&lt;/em>:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hugo new content posts/my-first-post.md
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>A markdown file was created in content/posts directory by Hugo. Open the file:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">---
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">title: &amp;#34;My First Post&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">date: 2023-07-19T17:51:29+09:00
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">draft: true
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">---
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Add some content to the body of the post and save the file.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">---
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">title: &amp;#34;My First Post&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">date: 2023-07-19T17:51:29+09:00
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">draft: true
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">---
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="gu">## Introduction
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="gu">&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Hello!
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">This is my first post.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Start Hugo’s development server again and have a look at the post:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hugo server -D
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="host-on-github-pages">Host on GitHub Pages&lt;/h2>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>A GitHub account is required for hosting site on GitHub Pages. &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/signup?source=login" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Sign up an account&lt;/a> if you don&amp;rsquo;t already have one.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Create a new repository&lt;/a>. A Pro(paid) account is needed to host site from private repository. So create a public repository if you want to host your site free.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://kediga.com/posts/how-to-create-a-personal-blog-using-hugo-and-github-pages/image1.png"
width="1454"
height="1472"
srcset="https://kediga.com/posts/how-to-create-a-personal-blog-using-hugo-and-github-pages/image1_hu150cd004d67592019f98a331f238c113_273611_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://kediga.com/posts/how-to-create-a-personal-blog-using-hugo-and-github-pages/image1_hu150cd004d67592019f98a331f238c113_273611_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Create a new repository"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="98"
data-flex-basis="237px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Push local repository of &lt;em>mysite&lt;/em> to GitHub:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
